    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Intermediary gem cut between the 8/8 and the brilliant. The crown and pavilion contain 16 facets and the table facet, but only one facet is polished on the rib of the pavilion instead of two.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
